#HYPERPARAMETERS:
#Oversampling:
over_proportion = 10 #denominator value of classification proportion, 2 -> 50%, 10 --> 10%, 20 -> 5% etc. 

#Training models:
lr_search = False #if True optimizing parameters for logreg model will be performed 
scoring_lr = 'recall'
param_grid_lr = {'C' : [0.1,1,10,100],
             'penalty' : ['l1','l2','elasticnet','none']}
svm_search = False #if True optimizing parameters for logreg model will be permofrmed 
scoring_svm = 'recall'
param_grid_svm = {'C' : [0.1,1,10,100],
             'kernel' : ['linear','rbf'],
             'gamma' : ['scale','auto']}
rf_search = False #if True optimizing parameters for logreg model will be performed 
scoring_rf = 'recall'
param_grid_rf = {'bootstrap': [True, False],
                 'max_depth': [5, 10, 20, 30, None],
                 'min_samples_leaf': [2, 5, 10],
                 'min_samples_split': [2, 5, 10],
                 'n_estimators': [100,200,400]}
xgb_search = False #if True optimizing parameters for logreg model will be performed 
scoring_xgb = 'recall'
param_grid_xgb = {'max_depth': [5, 10, 20, 30, None],
        'learning_rate': [0.1, 0.01, 0.001],
        'subsample': [0.5, 0.7, 1],
        'n_estimators' : [100,200,400]}

#Parameters if false:
lr_c = 1
lr_penalty = None

svm_c = 1
svm_kernel = 'rbf'
svm_gamma = 'auto'

rf_bootstrap = True
rf_max_depth = None
rf_min_samples_leaf = 1
rf_min_samples_split = 2
rf_n_estimators = 200

xgb_max_depth = 3
xgb_learning_rate = 0.1
xgb_subsample = 1
xgb_n_estimators = 200

use_same = True #if True once optimized parametres will be used also for extended model, False will perform second optimalization

#Reading data, droping text column
df = pd.read_csv('df_nlp_student.csv', index_col=0, sep=";", encoding='utf-8')
df.drop('text',axis=1)
fraud_X_df = df.drop(['text','#fraudulent'],axis=1)
fraud_Y_df = df['#fraudulent']
In [4]:
print("Initial distribution: ",sorted(Counter(fraud_Y_df).items()))
#Splitting set:
fraud_X_train, fraud_X_test, fraud_Y_train, fraud_Y_test = train_test_split(fraud_X_df, fraud_Y_df, test_size=0.25)

#Oversampling:
print("Distribution in training set before oversampling: ",sorted(Counter(fraud_Y_train).items()))
sampling_list = list(Counter(fraud_Y_train).items())
sample_strategy = {0: sampling_list[0][1], 1 : (round((sampling_list[0][1])/over_proportion))}
ros = RandomOverSampler(random_state=0, sampling_strategy=sample_strategy)
X_resampled, Y_resampled = ros.fit_resample(fraud_X_train, fraud_Y_train)
print("Distribution in training set after oversampling to {}%: {}".format((100/over_proportion),sorted(Counter(Y_resampled).items())))
print('Distribution in test set: ',sorted(Counter(fraud_Y_test).items()))

Initial distribution:  [(0, 8522), (1, 418)]
Distribution in training set before oversampling:  [(0, 6384), (1, 321)]
Distribution in training set after oversampling to 10.0%: [(0, 6384), (1, 638)]
Distribution in test set:  [(0, 2138), (1, 97)]
In [5]:
#Parameters optimalization (optional) and model training:
#1. Forest: 
if rf_search == True:
    grid_search_rf = GridSearchCV(RandomForestClassifier(),param_grid_rf,scoring=scoring_rf,cv=10)
    grid_search_rf.fit(X_resampled, Y_resampled)
    print('Best Parameters for Random Forest Model: ',grid_search_rf.best_params_)
    print('Best Score for Random Forest Model: ',grid_search_rf.best_score_)
    fraud_bm_forest = RandomForestClassifier(**grid_search_rf.best_params_)
else:
    fraud_bm_forest = RandomForestClassifier(bootstrap=rf_bootstrap,max_depth=rf_max_depth,min_samples_leaf=rf_min_samples_leaf,min_samples_split=rf_min_samples_split,n_estimators=rf_n_estimators)
fraud_bm_forest.fit(X_resampled, Y_resampled)

print('Finished training Random Forest model!')

#2. XGBoost:
if xgb_search == True:
    grid_search_xgb = GridSearchCV(GradientBoostingClassifier(),param_grid_xgb,scoring=scoring_xgb,cv=10)
    grid_search_xgb.fit(X_resampled, Y_resampled)
    print('Best Parameters for Random Forest Model: ',grid_search_xgb.best_params_)
    print('Best Score for Random Forest Model: ',grid_search_xgb.best_score_)
    fraud_bm_xgb = GradientBoostingClassifier(**grid_search_xgb.best_params_)
else:
    fraud_bm_xgb = GradientBoostingClassifier(max_depth=xgb_max_depth,learning_rate=xgb_learning_rate,subsample=xgb_subsample,n_estimators=xgb_n_estimators)

fraud_bm_xgb.fit(X_resampled, Y_resampled)
print('Finished training XGBoost model!')

#3. Logistic Regression:
if lr_search == True:
    grid_search_lr = GridSearchCV(LogisticRegression(),param_grid_lr,scoring=scoring_lr,cv=10)
    grid_search_lr.fit(X_resampled, Y_resampled)
    print('Best Parameters for Logistic Regression Model: ',grid_search_lr.best_params_)
    print('Best Score for Logistic Regression Model: ',grid_search_lr.best_score_)
    fraud_bm_logreg = LogisticRegression(**grid_search_lr.best_params_,max_iter=100000)
else:
    fraud_bm_logreg = LogisticRegression(C=lr_c,penalty=lr_penalty,max_iter=100000)

fraud_bm_logreg.fit(X_resampled, Y_resampled)
print('Finished training Logistic Regression model!')

#4. SVM:
if svm_search == True:
    grid_search_svm = GridSearchCV(SVC(random_state=42, probability=True), param_grid_svm, scoring=scoring_svm, cv=3)
    grid_search.fit(X_resampled, Y_resampled)
    print('Best Parameters for SVM Model: ',grid_search_svm.best_params_)
    print('Best Score for SVM Model: ',grid_search_svm.best_score_)
    fraud_bm_svm = SVC(**grid_search_svm.best_params_,random_state=42,probability=True)
else:
    fraud_bm_svm = SVC(C=svm_c,kernel=svm_kernel,gamma=svm_gamma,random_state=42,probability=True)
    
fraud_bm_svm.fit(X_resampled, Y_resampled)
print("Finished training SVM model!")

#Generating predictions for each model:
fraud_bm_rf_predict = fraud_bm_forest.predict(fraud_X_test)
fraud_bm_xgb_predict = fraud_bm_xgb.predict(fraud_X_test)
fraud_bm_lr_predict = fraud_bm_logreg.predict(fraud_X_test)
fraud_bm_svm_predict = fraud_bm_svm.predict(fraud_X_test)

Finished training Random Forest model!
Finished training XGBoost model!
Finished training Logistic Regression model!
Finished training SVM model!

roc_em_xgb = roc_auc_score(fraud_Y_test2,fraud_em_xgb_predict)

acc_em_svm = accuracy_score(fraud_Y_test2,fraud_em_svm_predict)
prec_em_svm = precision_score(fraud_Y_test2,fraud_em_svm_predict)
rec_em_svm = recall_score(fraud_Y_test2,fraud_em_svm_predict)
f1_em_svm = f1_score(fraud_Y_test2,fraud_em_svm_predict)
roc_em_svm = roc_auc_score(fraud_Y_test2,fraud_em_svm_predict)

acc_em_all = [acc_em_rf,acc_em_xgb,acc_em_lr,acc_em_svm]
prec_em_all = [prec_em_rf,prec_em_xgb,prec_em_lr,prec_em_svm]
rec_em_all = [rec_em_rf,rec_em_xgb,rec_em_lr,rec_em_svm]
f1_em_all = [f1_em_rf,f1_em_xgb,f1_em_lr,f1_em_svm]
roc_em_all = [roc_em_rf,roc_em_xgb,roc_em_lr,roc_em_svm]
